{"book": {"id": "daniel", "name": "Daniel", "osis": "Dan"}, "chapters": {"1": {"2": [{"anchor": {"anchor_index": 1, "char_offset": 160, "scope": "verse", "word_index": 31}, "marker": "a", "text": "That is, Babylonia"}], "3": [{"anchor": {"anchor_index": 1, "char_offset": 115, "scope": "verse", "word_index": 20}, "marker": "b", "text": "Hebrew from the seed of the kingdom"}], "4": [{"anchor": {"anchor_index": 1, "char_offset": 202, "scope": "verse", "word_index": 31}, "marker": "c", "text": "That is, the Babylonians"}]}, "10": {"1": [{"anchor": {"anchor_index": 1, "char_offset": 162, "scope": "verse", "word_index": 29}, "marker": "a", "text": "Or true and greatly burdensome"}], "16": [{"anchor": {"anchor_index": 1, "char_offset": 43, "scope": "verse", "word_index": 9}, "marker": "b", "text": "Most MT manuscripts; literally with the likeness of sons of man ; DSS, LXX, and one MT manuscript with the likeness of the hand of a man"}], "20": [{"anchor": {"anchor_index": 1, "char_offset": 165, "scope": "verse", "word_index": 34}, "marker": "c", "text": "Hebrew of Javan"}]}, "11": {"13": [{"anchor": {"anchor_index": 1, "char_offset": 94, "scope": "verse", "word_index": 18}, "marker": "e", "text": "Hebrew at the end of the times"}], "17": [{"anchor": {"anchor_index": 1, "char_offset": 237, "scope": "verse", "word_index": 46}, "marker": "f", "text": "Or but she will not stand with him or support him"}], "2": [{"anchor": {"anchor_index": 1, "char_offset": 222, "scope": "verse", "word_index": 44}, "marker": "a", "text": "Hebrew of Javan"}], "30": [{"anchor": {"anchor_index": 1, "char_offset": 15, "scope": "verse", "word_index": 3}, "marker": "g", "text": "Or western coastlands or Mediterranean islands"}], "39": [{"anchor": {"anchor_index": 1, "char_offset": 188, "scope": "verse", "word_index": 33}, "marker": "h", "text": "Or for a reward"}], "40": [{"anchor": {"anchor_index": 1, "char_offset": 72, "scope": "verse", "word_index": 16}, "marker": "i", "text": "Hebrew will thrust at him"}], "43": [{"anchor": {"anchor_index": 1, "char_offset": 119, "scope": "verse", "word_index": 23}, "marker": "j", "text": "That is, people from the upper Nile region"}], "44": [{"anchor": {"anchor_index": 1, "char_offset": 135, "scope": "verse", "word_index": 27}, "marker": "k", "text": "Forms of the Hebrew cherem refer to the giving over of things or persons, either by destroying them or by giving them as an offering."}], "6": [{"anchor": {"anchor_index": 1, "char_offset": 220, "scope": "verse", "word_index": 43}, "marker": "b", "text": "Or offspring"}, {"anchor": {"anchor_index": 2, "char_offset": 306, "scope": "verse", "word_index": 60}, "marker": "c", "text": "Or child ; see Vulgate and Syriac."}], "7": [{"anchor": {"anchor_index": 1, "char_offset": 28, "scope": "verse", "word_index": 6}, "marker": "d", "text": "Literally a branch from her roots"}]}, "12": {"2": [{"anchor": {"anchor_index": 1, "char_offset": 127, "scope": "verse", "word_index": 23}, "marker": "a", "text": "See John 5:29 and Revelation 11:18."}], "3": [{"anchor": {"anchor_index": 1, "char_offset": 60, "scope": "verse", "word_index": 11}, "marker": "b", "text": "Or expanse or firmament ; see also Genesis 1:6–8."}, {"anchor": {"anchor_index": 2, "char_offset": 145, "scope": "verse", "word_index": 26}, "marker": "c", "text": "See Matthew 13:43."}]}, "2": {"2": [{"anchor": {"anchor_index": 1, "char_offset": 87, "scope": "verse", "word_index": 13}, "marker": "a", "text": "Or Chaldeans ; also in verses 4, 5, and 10"}], "31": [{"anchor": {"anchor_index": 1, "char_offset": 45, "scope": "verse", "word_index": 9}, "marker": "c", "text": "Or image ; here and through the rest of Daniel 2"}], "34": [{"anchor": {"anchor_index": 1, "char_offset": 36, "scope": "verse", "word_index": 8}, "marker": "d", "text": "LXX cut out from a mountain"}], "4": [{"anchor": {"anchor_index": 1, "char_offset": 50, "scope": "verse", "word_index": 8}, "marker": "b", "text": "The original text from this point of Daniel 2:4 through Daniel 7:28 is in Aramaic."}], "43": [{"anchor": {"anchor_index": 1, "char_offset": 51, "scope": "verse", "word_index": 11}, "marker": "e", "text": "Aramaic the seed of men"}]}, "3": {"1": [{"anchor": {"anchor_index": 1, "char_offset": 40, "scope": "verse", "word_index": 6}, "marker": "a", "text": "Or image ; here and throughout Daniel 3"}, {"anchor": {"anchor_index": 2, "char_offset": 79, "scope": "verse", "word_index": 13}, "marker": "b", "text": "The statue was approximately 90 feet high and 9 feet wide (27.4 meters high and 2.7 meters wide)."}], "17": [{"anchor": {"anchor_index": 1, "char_offset": 48, "scope": "verse", "word_index": 11}, "marker": "e", "text": "Or If this be so, then the God whom serve is able"}], "25": [{"anchor": {"anchor_index": 1, "char_offset": 132, "scope": "verse", "word_index": 24}, "marker": "f", "text": "Or like the Son of God"}], "28": [{"anchor": {"anchor_index": 1, "char_offset": 103, "scope": "verse", "word_index": 16}, "marker": "g", "text": "Or Angel"}], "5": [{"anchor": {"anchor_index": 1, "char_offset": 100, "scope": "verse", "word_index": 20}, "marker": "c", "text": "The precise identification of some musical instruments in this chapter is uncertain."}], "8": [{"anchor": {"anchor_index": 1, "char_offset": 29, "scope": "verse", "word_index": 5}, "marker": "d", "text": "Or Chaldeans"}]}, "4": {"13": [{"anchor": {"anchor_index": 1, "char_offset": 67, "scope": "verse", "word_index": 17}, "marker": "b", "text": "Or an angelic watcher or a messenger ; also in verses 17 and 23"}], "7": [{"anchor": {"anchor_index": 1, "char_offset": 44, "scope": "verse", "word_index": 5}, "marker": "a", "text": "Or Chaldeans"}]}, "5": {"1": [{"anchor": {"anchor_index": 1, "char_offset": 6, "scope": "verse", "word_index": 1}, "marker": "a", "text": "Aramaic does not include Later . Some translators include Many years later to account for the time elapsed, probably about 30 years, since the previous chapter."}], "10": [{"anchor": {"anchor_index": 1, "char_offset": 56, "scope": "verse", "word_index": 11}, "marker": "d", "text": "Or queen mother"}], "2": [{"anchor": {"anchor_index": 1, "char_offset": 126, "scope": "verse", "word_index": 21}, "marker": "b", "text": "Or predecessor or grandfather ; also in verses 11, 13, and 18"}], "22": [{"anchor": {"anchor_index": 1, "char_offset": 16, "scope": "verse", "word_index": 4}, "marker": "e", "text": "Or descendant or successor or grandson"}], "26": [{"anchor": {"anchor_index": 1, "char_offset": 51, "scope": "verse", "word_index": 9}, "marker": "f", "text": "Mene sounds like the Aramaic for numbered ."}], "27": [{"anchor": {"anchor_index": 1, "char_offset": 5, "scope": "verse", "word_index": 1}, "marker": "g", "text": "Tekel sounds like the Aramaic for weighed ."}], "28": [{"anchor": {"anchor_index": 1, "char_offset": 5, "scope": "verse", "word_index": 1}, "marker": "h", "text": "Peres (the singular of Parsin ) sounds like the Aramaic for divided and for Persia ."}], "30": [{"anchor": {"anchor_index": 1, "char_offset": 48, "scope": "verse", "word_index": 8}, "marker": "i", "text": "That is, the Babylonians"}], "7": [{"anchor": {"anchor_index": 1, "char_offset": 52, "scope": "verse", "word_index": 8}, "marker": "c", "text": "Or Chaldeans ; also in verse 11"}]}, "6": {"28": [{"anchor": {"anchor_index": 1, "char_offset": 69, "scope": "verse", "word_index": 13}, "marker": "a", "text": "Or prospered during the reign of Darius, that is, the reign of Cyrus"}]}, "7": {"13": [{"anchor": {"anchor_index": 1, "char_offset": 81, "scope": "verse", "word_index": 19}, "marker": "b", "text": "Or one like a son of man"}, {"anchor": {"anchor_index": 2, "char_offset": 115, "scope": "verse", "word_index": 25}, "marker": "c", "text": "See Matthew 24:30, Matthew 26:64, Mark 13:26, Mark 14:62, Luke 21:27, Revelation 1:13, and Revelation 14:14."}], "2": [{"anchor": {"anchor_index": 1, "char_offset": 123, "scope": "verse", "word_index": 23}, "marker": "a", "text": "Perhaps the Great Sea , that is, the Mediterranean Sea"}]}, "8": {"12": [{"anchor": {"anchor_index": 1, "char_offset": 21, "scope": "verse", "word_index": 4}, "marker": "a", "text": "Or on account of transgression"}], "21": [{"anchor": {"anchor_index": 1, "char_offset": 46, "scope": "verse", "word_index": 8}, "marker": "b", "text": "Hebrew of Javan"}]}, "9": {"1": [{"anchor": {"anchor_index": 1, "char_offset": 42, "scope": "verse", "word_index": 9}, "marker": "a", "text": "Hebrew Ahasuerus"}, {"anchor": {"anchor_index": 2, "char_offset": 114, "scope": "verse", "word_index": 23}, "marker": "b", "text": "That is, the Babylonians"}], "2": [{"anchor": {"anchor_index": 1, "char_offset": 194, "scope": "verse", "word_index": 34}, "marker": "c", "text": "See Jeremiah 25:11–12 and Jeremiah 29:10."}], "24": [{"anchor": {"anchor_index": 1, "char_offset": 13, "scope": "verse", "word_index": 2}, "marker": "e", "text": "Or Seventy sevens ; also twice in verse 25 and once in verse 26"}, {"anchor": {"anchor_index": 2, "char_offset": 249, "scope": "verse", "word_index": 44}, "marker": "f", "text": "Or the Holy of Holies or the Most Holy One ; literally the Most Holy"}], "25": [{"anchor": {"anchor_index": 1, "char_offset": 110, "scope": "verse", "word_index": 18}, "marker": "g", "text": "Or the Anointed One ; also in verse 26"}], "26": [{"anchor": {"anchor_index": 1, "char_offset": 30, "scope": "verse", "word_index": 5}, "marker": "h", "text": "Hebrew Then after sixty-two sevens"}], "27": [{"anchor": {"anchor_index": 1, "char_offset": 54, "scope": "verse", "word_index": 11}, "marker": "i", "text": "Or for one seven ; similarly again in this verse"}, {"anchor": {"anchor_index": 2, "char_offset": 210, "scope": "verse", "word_index": 41}, "marker": "j", "text": "Literally And on the wing (will come) the abomination that causes desolation, or And on the wing of abominations (will come) one who causes desolation,"}, {"anchor": {"anchor_index": 3, "char_offset": 264, "scope": "verse", "word_index": 50}, "marker": "k", "text": "Literally until the decreed consummation is poured out upon (him who) is desolate."}], "4": [{"anchor": {"anchor_index": 1, "char_offset": 125, "scope": "verse", "word_index": 24}, "marker": "d", "text": "Forms of the Hebrew chesed are translated here and in most cases throughout the Scriptures as loving devotion ; the range of meaning includes love , goodness , kindness , faithfulness , and mercy , as well as loyalty to a covenant ."}]}}, "translation": {"code": "BSB", "id": "bsb", "name": "Berean Study Bible"}}